{"tid":1365730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[起底搵證據] 何妖關聯公司","createTime":"2019-07-25T17:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T17:34:55.000Z","uid":288414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acc051e5f18ed7a688d37784b1c631a0976cdbb1","tid":1365730,"uid":288414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:29:07.000Z","msg":"其實西環喺幕後指使呢樣嘢就呼之肉出。出一晚 5-600 人每人一兩千連聯絡費都要 100萬起跳，計埋班中間人大佬濕腳大拿拿吹一晚雞隨時 2-300 萬，試問今時今日圍村行古惑邊有咁闊佬。西環話唔關佢地事，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中聯辦部長李薊貽</span></span></strong> 都話唔關佢事，咁d 錢一定喺何妖自己出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西環幕後操控香港維穩就喺靠用國企牌頭向刀手射錢，唔知何律師家族公司呢排有無做咩國企生意呢？大家巴打點睇？"},{"pid":"4a19bfd3f17f73bbd0dd6547b45a0ade3f8b68cf","tid":1365730,"uid":288414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:34:55.000Z","msg":"推推"}]}